title: Everyone Hates Gov. Whitmer (D-MI) | Ep #9 Good Morning MugClub
description: What do you think about Gov. Whitmer's ban of private and public gatherings, is this government overreach? We discuss the situation in Michigan, give some updates on COVID and Trump's guidelines for re-opening America, and laugh our asses off at a recent ABC special.
